John E. Hagale  Independent Director, Oasis Petroleum Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships60$97,735
Background

		Mr. John E. Hagale served as the Chief Financial Officer of Rosetta Resources, Inc. from November 9, 2011 to July 2015 and served as its Executive Vice President from October 24, 2011 to July 2015. Mr. Hagale lead the Financial, Accounting, Tax, Investor Relations, Marketing and Trading Functions. He served as Treasurer of Rosetta Resources, Inc. from November 9, 2011 to August 2012. He has more than 30 years of financial experience in oil and gas and healthcare. He ... was also employed with Burlington Resources Inc. and its predecessor Burlington Northern Inc. for 15 years where he held a series of executive financial positions. He served as an Executive Vice President of Burlington Resources Inc. since December 1995 and served as its Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer of Burlington Resources Oil & Gas Company since March 1993; Chief Financial Officer since April 1994, Senior Vice President from April 1994 to December 1995 and Vice President of Finance from March 1992 to February 1993. Mr. Hagale served as Executive Vice President, Chief Financial Officer and Chief Administrative Officer of The Methodist Hospital System from June 2003 to October 2011. He began his career with Deloitte Haskins and Sells. He has been an Independent Director of Oasis Petroleum Inc. since July 27, 2016. He has been an Independent Director at Cobalt International Energy, Inc. since March 1, 2016. Mr. Hagale holds a Bachelor of Business Administration degree in Accounting from the University of Notre Dame. He is a Certified Public Accountant.Read Full Background




